    "Equitable access also includes the sharing of best practices and case studies that narrate success stories on the use of AI in education and potential drawbacks.",
    "It should be made clear at this point that inequalities in AI-integration are not the foci of the paper, but they are an interesting find from our results.",
    "The study by Brown (2022) explored the relationship between academic integrity and the digital divide that constrains equal access to technology.",
